ygData.subject: Re: My new weapons!! =)
ygData.msgSnippet: Heh extremly good deal on both acounts. You really got a Yak for only a full suite of Lambent? I m impressed. The runed falchion goes for 3k pp on E ci roughly
ygData.messageBody:
Heh extremly good deal on both acounts. You really got a Yak for only a
full suite of Lambent? I'm impressed. The runed falchion goes for 3k pp on
E'ci roughly so you got off good on both acounts.

Naeeldar

>Over the weekend I got a Ykesha, traded all my Lambent for it and then

>
